mixin notFound()  
    div(class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center vh-100")
        div(class="text-center")
            h1(class="display-1 fw-bold") 404
            p(class="fs-3")
                span(class="text-danger") Opps!Page not found
            p(class="lead") The page you’re looking for doesn’t exist.
            a(href="/posts" class="btn btn-primary") Go Home